name: Benjamin COOPER, Petitioner v. Honorable Judge Sheila WOODS-SKIPPER President Judge, Philadelphia County, Respondent

parties: Benjamin COOPER, Petitioner v. Honorable Judge Sheila WOODS-SKIPPER President Judge, Philadelphia County, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of July, 2010, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. Our Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

Benjamin COOPER, Petitioner v. Honorable Judge Sheila WOODS-SKIPPER President Judge, Philadelphia County, Respondent.

July 29, 2010.
